Privacy Policy

Last Updated: August 27, 2025

Thank you for using the "Dicto" Chrome extension. Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy outlines how we handle your information to ensure transparency and trust.

### Information We Collect

We do not collect, store, or share any personal data or browsing activity. The "Dicto" extension operates entirely within your browser, ensuring that no data is transmitted to external servers.

### Permissions

The extension may request certain permissions, such as access to your tabs or storage, to function properly. These permissions are strictly used to provide the intended functionality and are never used for data collection purposes.

### Third-Party Services

The "Dicto" extension does not integrate with any third-party services or analytics tools. Your data remains private and secure within your browser.

### Contact Us

If you have any questions, feedback, or concerns about this Privacy Policy, feel free to reach out to us at: **longnghia2.00@gmail.com**

### Changes to This Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy periodically to reflect changes in our practices or for other operational, legal, or regulatory reasons. Any updates will be communicated within the extension or on our official website.

By using the "Dicto" Chrome extension, you acknowledge and agree to this Privacy Policy.
